195
00:12:57,641 --> 00:13:00,961
{No one heard, even in rumors,
that the bounty was claimed.}Tak ada yang mendengarnya, bahkan menurut rumornya, hadiah buronannya sudah diambil.

196
00:13:00,961 --> 00:13:03,631
{Did someone obliterate them?}Apa seseorang memusnahkan mereka?

197
00:13:03,631 --> 00:13:06,561
Yang kami tahu, tidak banyak yang selamat.

198
00:13:10,771 --> 00:13:13,361
{Th-The leader of the Band
of the Hawk was Griffith.}Pe-Pemimpin Perkumpulan Elang adalah Griffith.

199
00:13:13,361 --> 00:13:15,301
{After he went missing,}Setelah dia menghilang,

200
00:13:15,301 --> 00:13:18,411
{it's said a woman replaced
