201
00:13:20,551 --> 00:13:22,761
{It's also said that the captain of their raiders}Juga dikatakan kalau kapten perampok mereka

202
00:13:22,761 --> 00:13:26,451
{wielded a massive sword and could
slay a hundred men with ease.}punya pedang besar dan bisa menebas seratus orang dengan mudah.

203
00:13:26,881 --> 00:13:29,241
{You seem to match his description.}Kau kelihatan cocok dengan deskripsi ini.

204
00:13:29,241 --> 00:13:31,041
{And if I recall, his name was...}Dan kalau kuingat, nama dia adalah...

205
00:13:31,711 --> 00:13:32,771
{Also...}Juga...

206
00:13:33,881 --> 00:13:35,141
{A questionable item,}Hal yang harus ditanyakan,

207
00:13:35,711 --> 00:13:39,711
benda yang bisa dianggap sebagai kepemilikan sesat...

208
00:13:40,561 --> 00:13:41,971
{Nice, isn't it?}Bagus, 'kan?

209
00:13:46,961 --> 00:13:49,121
{If this is a heathen idol,}Kalau benda ini adalah sesembahan kaum kafir,

210
00:13:49,121 --> 00:13:52,001
{you will be tried as a heretic.}kau akan dianggap menjadi kaum pendukung sesat.

211
00:13:52,001 --> 00:13:55,611
{If you do not wish to endure that,
you should confess everything now.}Kalau tak ingin dianggap demikian,
kau harus mengakui semuanya sekarang.

212
00:13:55,611 --> 00:13:57,331
{Is that not preferable to}Bukannya tidak enak kalau

213
00:13:57,331 --> 00:14:00,211
{being interrogated under torture,
then burned at the stake?}diintrograsi sambil disiksa, kemudian dibakar di tiang?

214
00:14:00,721 --> 00:14:02,661
{Answer me, cur!}Jawab aku, keparat!

215
00:14:02,991 --> 00:14:06,491
{Do you believe in God and the devil?}Apa kau percaya pada Tuhan dan iblis?

216
00:14:06,491 --> 00:14:08,011
{What's your point?}Apa maksudmu?

217
00:14:08,011 --> 00:14:09,981
{Are you trying to blaspheme yet again?}Apa kau mencoba menistakan Tuhan lagi?

218
00:14:09,981 --> 00:14:11,831
{Have you ever met God?}Apa kau pernah bertemu Tuhan?

219
00:14:12,641 --> 00:14:16,681
{God does not show us His miraculous
existence on this Earth so easily.}Tuhan takkan memperlihatkan wujud sucinya di dunia ini dengan mudah.

220
00:14:17,101 --> 00:14:20,121
{Through our faith, God is always with us.}Melalui iman kami, Tuhan selalu bersama kami.

221
00:14:20,121 --> 00:14:23,421
{In our souls and up in Heaven.}Di dalam jiwa kami dan di atas Surga.

222
00:14:25,491 --> 00:14:27,431
{Wh-Why do you laugh?}Ke-Kenapa kau tertawa?

223
00:14:27,431 --> 00:14:29,591
{What a picture-perfect response.}Respon yang kelihatan sempurna.

224
00:14:29,591 --> 00:14:31,571
{Did you learn that in a convent?}Apa kau mempelajari itu di biara?

225
00:14:32,081 --> 00:14:34,941
{On a battlefield, a nobleman
said the exact same thing,}Dia medan perang, bangsawan juga mengatakan hal yang sama,

226
00:14:34,941 --> 00:14:37,971
{burning a city to the ground,
with its women and children.}selama membakar kota sampa hancur, bersama wanita dan anak-anak.

227
00:14:38,301 --> 00:14:42,091
{I'm not talking about some shitty, useless god}Aku bukan mengatakan suatu hal yang buruk, tuhan yang tak berguna

228
00:14:42,091 --> 00:14:44,951
{who's just an empty decoration.}yang hanya sebuah dekorasi belaka.

229
00:14:46,171 --> 00:14:48,561
{A confession would be a waste of time.}Pengakuan hanya membuang waktu.

230
00:14:48,561 --> 00:14:50,521
{I have no intention of repenting,}Aku tak mau bertobat,

231
00:14:50,521 --> 00:14:53,761
{and I don't think you'll learn
anything, even if I told you.}dan menurutku kau takkan mengerti apapun, walau aku bilang padamu.

232
00:14:53,761 --> 00:14:57,461
Doakan saja aku di kuil yang reyot.

233
00:14:57,461 --> 00:15:00,451
Brengsek!

234
00:15:02,101 --> 00:15:03,591
Berani sekali!

235
00:15:03,591 --> 00:15:04,711
{Cur,}Bajingan,

236
00:15:04,711 --> 00:15:07,391
{how dare you blaspheme in front of me,}beraninya kau menistakan di depanku,

237
00:15:07,391 --> 00:15:11,101
{Commander of the Holy Iron Chain Knights?}Komandan Kesatria Rantai Besi Kudus?

238
00:15:11,101 --> 00:15:13,151
{I was prepared to show mercy,}Aku berencana mengasihanimu,

239
00:15:13,151 --> 00:15:17,901
{in consideration of your
injuries, but no longer!}karena mengkhawatirkan lukamu, tapi sekarang sudah tidak lagi!

240
00:15:17,901 --> 00:15:20,041
{I shall make you talk,}Aku akan membuatmu mengaku,

241
00:15:20,041 --> 00:15:22,291
{even if it means flaying
the skin from your body!}walau harus menguliti kulitmu!

242
00:15:22,291 --> 00:15:24,141
{I swear this by my faith!}Aku bersumpah atas kepercayaanku!

243
00:15:24,141 --> 00:15:26,241
{You're trying way too hard, aren't you?}Kau sudah mencoba dengan keras, ya?

244
00:15:27,031 --> 00:15:29,031
{Be it God or your rank,}Mau Tuhan atau kedudukanmu,

245
00:15:29,031 --> 00:15:32,651
{whatever weight you're trying to
throw around won't earn loyalty.}apapun yang coba kau lakukan takkan mendapatkan kesetiaan apapun.

246
00:15:32,651 --> 00:15:34,721
{Not like that Knight of the Bridge commands.}Seperti perintah Ksatria Jembatan.

247
00:15:35,171 --> 00:15:37,041
Kalau kau tanya aku,

248
00:15:37,041 --> 00:15:41,731
{you're just like that idol you
worship, all empty inside.}kau sama kosongnya dengan tuhan yang kau sembah.

249
00:15:47,851 --> 00:15:49,011
{You...}Kau...

250
00:15:49,011 --> 00:15:50,111
Kau!

251
00:15:53,771 --> 00:15:55,561
Beraninya sekali!

252
00:16:19,561 --> 00:16:20,961
Nona Farnese!

253
00:16:21,471 --> 00:16:23,791
Permisi... Apa yang barusan terjadi?

254
00:16:23,791 --> 00:16:26,581
Nona Farnese, apa maksudnya ini?

255
00:16:26,581 --> 00:16:28,131
Ribut-ribut apa ini?

256
00:16:28,131 --> 00:16:30,081
Aku hanya bertanya,

257
00:16:30,081 --> 00:16:32,791
sebelum kita mengirim dia ke Takhta Suci.

258
00:16:32,791 --> 00:16:34,371
Tapi, ini...

259
00:16:34,371 --> 00:16:35,571
Aku sudah selesai.

260
00:16:35,571 --> 00:16:37,161
Kembalikan dia ke dalam selnya.

261
00:16:37,161 --> 00:16:38,721
Kalian juga pergilah.

262
00:16:38,721 --> 00:16:40,021
Nona Farnese...

263
00:16:40,021 --> 00:16:41,041
Kau tak mendengarku?

264
00:16:41,041 --> 00:16:42,411
Sudah kubilang, pergilah.

265
00:16:44,331 --> 00:16:45,441
Baik.

266
00:16:45,441 --> 00:16:46,871
Jangan memborgolnya.

267
00:16:46,871 --> 00:16:48,811
Rawat semua lukanya, dan kurung dia di penjara.

268
00:16:48,811 --> 00:16:49,931
Bawa dia!

269
00:16:49,931 --> 00:16:51,931
Baik, tuan!

270
00:16:53,441 --> 00:16:56,711
Kumohon, jangan kasar pada komandan kami.

271
00:16:57,521 --> 00:17:00,831
Meski kelihatannya begitu,
sebenarnya dia cukup cantik.

272
00:17:18,721 --> 00:17:21,741
Aku tak boleh membuang waktuku di sini.

273
00:17:21,741 --> 00:17:23,741
Sial.

274
00:17:24,381 --> 00:17:27,071
Aku tak punya waktu bermain
dengan orang-orang barbar ini.

275
00:17:29,531 --> 00:17:31,531
Casca...

276
00:17:33,311 --> 00:17:34,471
Dan...

277
00:17:36,121 --> 00:17:37,361
Ini hampir waktunya.

278
00:17:42,011 --> 00:17:43,081
Sial.

279
00:17:47,071 --> 00:17:48,581
Tak bersenjata dan dipenjara,

280
00:17:48,981 --> 00:17:50,731
apalagi dalam kondisi yang buruk.

281
00:17:50,731 --> 00:17:52,731
Apa yang harus kulakukan?

282
00:17:52,601 --> 00:17:54,091
Hup!

283
00:17:54,771 --> 00:17:57,041
Sepertinya aku harus menggunakan orang ini.

284
00:17:57,041 --> 00:17:58,951
Aku di sini untuk menyelamatkanmu, Guts.

285
00:17:58,951 --> 00:18:01,171
Lihat, kau bisa keluar dengan kunci ini.

286
00:18:01,471 --> 00:18:03,471
Kenapa kau ada di sini?

287
00:18:02,961 --> 00:18:05,191
Para Elf punya rasa tanggung jawab yang kuat.

288
00:18:07,851 --> 00:18:09,191
Apa yang akan kau lakukan?

289
00:18:09,641 --> 00:18:11,531
Mengambil barang-barangku kembali.

290
00:18:11,531 --> 00:18:13,151
Cuma itu milikku.

291
00:18:16,461 --> 00:18:19,331
Tapi senjatamu masih ada di kemah para wanita.

292
00:18:19,601 --> 00:18:20,841
Sempurna.

293
00:18:20,841 --> 00:18:22,761
Tergantung situasinya, kita bisa membawa sandera.

294
00:18:24,521 --> 00:18:28,231
Aku tidak peduli kalau harus membunuh banyak orang dari mereka.

295
00:18:29,391 --> 00:18:32,721
Bagaimanapun, ada seseorang yang harus kutemukan.

296
00:18:33,161 --> 00:18:36,421
Aku tak peduli pada mereka yang akan menghalangiku.

297
00:18:57,801 --> 00:18:59,551
Apa yang terjadi?

298
00:19:11,351 --> 00:19:14,591
Oh, tuhan... tolong beri aku petunjuk.

299
00:19:17,991 --> 00:19:19,101
Kau!

300
00:19:21,401 --> 00:19:22,561
Oh...

301
00:19:22,561 --> 00:19:24,421
Mempesona, bukan?

302
00:19:31,191 --> 00:19:32,921
Lukamu sangat parah.

303
00:19:32,921 --> 00:19:35,941
Jangan tergesa-gesa menggunakan pedangmu, nanti lukamu bisa makin parah.

304
00:19:38,281 --> 00:19:39,811
Setengah kekuatakanku masih tersisa.

305
00:19:39,811 --> 00:19:41,231
Nona Farnese, kita dalam keadaan darurat.

306
00:19:41,231 --> 00:19:42,621
Si pendekar hitam sudah...

307
00:19:42,621 --> 00:19:44,621
Kau—

308
00:19:44,391 --> 00:19:45,621
Kejam sekali.

309
00:19:45,621 --> 00:19:49,261
Kalau sudah begini, kurasa aku harus bertanya padanya saja.

310
00:19:58,151 --> 00:20:00,151
Kebakaran!

311
00:19:58,861 --> 00:20:00,491
Pendekar hitam sudah melarikan diri!

312
00:20:00,491 --> 00:20:02,501
Hentikan apinya agar tidak menyebar ke tenda lain!

313
00:20:02,501 --> 00:20:03,971
Nona Farnese!

314
00:20:04,951 --> 00:20:06,021
Kau...

315
00:20:06,021 --> 00:20:07,231
Bagaimana kau...

316
00:20:07,761 --> 00:20:09,981
Menyingkirlah, kek.

317
00:20:09,981 --> 00:20:13,281
Kau pikir bisa melarikan diri dengan luka seperti itu?

318
00:20:13,281 --> 00:20:14,431
Entahlah.

319
00:20:14,431 --> 00:20:17,871
Praktik membakar orang mati tidak diperuntukkan hanya bagi para pendeta, bukan?

320
00:20:17,871 --> 00:20:19,871
Bagaimana?

321
00:20:18,871 --> 00:20:20,611
Aku akan membakar pantatnya.

322
00:20:20,611 --> 00:20:24,321
Memakai sandera... Kau memang pengecut!

323
00:20:24,321 --> 00:20:25,821
Kami sudah tak punya pilihan.

324
00:20:25,821 --> 00:20:27,441
Kalian semua, mundurlah.

325
00:20:27,441 --> 00:20:28,601
Maaf.

326
00:20:33,651 --> 00:20:35,411
Apa yang sudah kau lakukan?

327
00:20:36,151 --> 00:20:37,341
Jangan khawatir.

328
00:20:40,761 --> 00:20:41,841
Cepat!

329
00:20:41,841 --> 00:20:43,481
Kumpulkan kudanya!

330
00:20:43,481 --> 00:20:45,151
Kesalahan ini belum terlalu dalam.

331
00:20:45,151 --> 00:20:47,311
Kita tidak boleh membiarkannya lolos!

332
00:20:49,351 --> 00:20:50,421
Siapa itu?

333
00:20:55,691 --> 00:20:58,281
Kau luar biasa.

334
00:20:58,281 --> 00:21:02,121
Pada siapa kau harus berterima kasih
karena sudah membawamu sejauh ini?

335
00:21:02,121 --> 00:21:04,121
Kuda.

336
00:21:02,951 --> 00:21:04,871
Lalu meminta maaf pada kuda.

337
00:21:04,871 --> 00:21:06,201
Maaf ya, kuda.

338
00:21:06,201 --> 00:21:07,941
Selama kau mengingat itu.

339
00:21:09,011 --> 00:21:11,011
Hei.

340
00:21:10,001 --> 00:21:11,721
Keadaan sudah berbalik, ya?

341
00:21:12,081 --> 00:21:13,651
Jangan memberontak...

342
00:21:13,651 --> 00:21:16,091
Dengan tangan terikat, kalau kau
jatuh, kau akan mati!

343
00:21:16,091 --> 00:21:17,181
Jangan khawatir.

344
00:21:17,181 --> 00:21:18,521
Kami tidak akan memakanmu.

345
00:21:18,521 --> 00:21:19,861
Oh, aku Puck.

346
00:21:20,981 --> 00:21:22,081
Lepaskan aku, pengecut!

347
00:21:22,081 --> 00:21:26,241
Beraninya kau mengatakan itu pada
Komandan Kesatria Rantai Besi Kudus—

348
00:21:26,241 --> 00:21:28,241
Berisik.

349
00:21:27,221 --> 00:21:29,221
Oh, hei!

350
00:21:27,951 --> 00:21:30,561
Terus banyak cakap,
hanya akan membuatmu menyesal.

351
00:21:30,561 --> 00:21:32,601
Maaf, kau akan kubawa.

352
00:21:33,021 --> 00:21:34,481
Dan aku ingin menanyakan sesuatu!

353
00:21:34,481 --> 00:21:35,661
Ini penghinaan!

354
00:21:35,951 --> 00:21:37,901
Bagaimana cara orang itu melakukannya?

355
00:21:37,901 --> 00:21:39,061
Turunkan aku!

356
00:21:39,061 --> 00:21:43,091
Aku lebih memilih mati daripada harus mendengarkanmu!

357
00:21:43,681 --> 00:21:45,791
Tidak!

358
00:21:46,081 --> 00:21:48,121
Bisa kau tenang sebentar?

359
00:21:48,121 --> 00:21:50,971
Dasar, tak bisakah dia untuk
mencintai sesama manusia?

360
00:21:50,971 --> 00:21:52,971
Tidak.

361
00:21:51,811 --> 00:21:54,021
Maaf, nona.

362
00:21:58,461 --> 00:22:00,921
Beraninya kau? Jangan mempermainkanku!

363
00:22:00,921 --> 00:22:02,351
Apa yang kau lakukan?

364
00:22:02,351 --> 00:22:03,371
Dia tak melihatnya.

365
00:22:03,371 --> 00:22:05,371
Huh?

366
00:22:03,881 --> 00:22:05,461
Dia tidak mencoba untuk melihatku.

367
00:22:05,461 --> 00:22:06,541
Dia tidak...

368
00:22:06,541 --> 00:22:09,771
Dia tidak bisa melihat para Elf.

369
00:23:57,121 --> 00:24:01,541
Episode berikutnya

370
00:24:03,541 --> 00:24:05,541
<font size="35">Apa ini ada hubungannya dengan Nubuat yang diramalkan?</font>

371
00:24:07,301 --> 00:24:09,631
Jadilah anjing yang baik.

372
00:24:11,591 --> 00:24:13,591
<font size="35">Aku baru saja ingat untuk pertama kalinya...</font>

373
00:24:15,601 --> 00:24:17,601
<font size="35">Para manusia yang melawan kita hanyalah makanan.</font>

